name: AGOQ 19.5
description:
For time:

•30 snatches
•30 strict handstand push-ups

Time cap: 6 minutes

Ages 16-17 and 35-54:
Men use 135 lb.
Women use 95 lb.

Ages 14-15:
Boys use 95 lb.
Girls use 65 lb.

Ages 55+:
Men use 95 lb. and perform 5-in. elevated strict HSPU.
Women use 65 lb. and perform 5-in. elevated strict
HSPU.
